"          <li>quality of construction (e.g. materials used for wall, floor "
"and roof);</li>\n"
"          <li>compliance with local building codes, standards and "
"bylaws.</li>\n"
"        </ul>\n"
"        <p><em>Sufficient living area / Overcrowding:</em></p>\n"
"        <ul>\n"
"          <li>Proportion of households with more than two persons per "
"room.</li>\n"
"        </ul>\n"
